ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectCamrose Chamber of Commerce (Alberta) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CAMROSE CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in Alberta, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the Camrose electoral district to the limits of the City of Camrose, in the Camrose County, including the areas up to Highway #617 North to Highway #609 South, and Highway #21 West across to Highway #854 East.
